dct_title_s: Austria. Plan von Salzburg. G.S.G.S. no.4483
dct_description_sm: Great Britain. War Office. Geographical Section. General Staff . G.S.G.S. no.4483. Inset: "The Old City" (1:7,500)."Reproduced from and Austrian plan dated 1936. Legend printed in German and English. In lower margin: "Laut Erlass des Landeschulrates Salzburg vom 20. Juli 1936, Z.2603/a zum; Gebrauch fur dem heimatkundlichen Unterricht an den Schulen zugelassen." In lower left margin: "I/Nov. 44/66IE/6AG 7050." In lower right margin: "U.S. Army 1944.".
